Name: Nobility
Desc:
Act upon the nobility to sacrifice your life for another. Receives partial damage for party members including yourself while inside the domain your created and creates a shield based on the damage.
This skill isn't affected by the Buff Duration Bonus effect and is immediately canceled upon using again.
Lv. 10 Effect: Can learn the 5th Advancement Skill, Restore.

H.Old:
MP Cost: 200. Creates a domain for 20 sec.
Receives 30% of the damage dealt to party members inside the domain in their place and creates a shield for 80% of that damage
You cannot receive if the damage received instead is greater than the remaining HP.
Cooldown 180 sec.
